♫ All are just illusions ♫

491
00:43:37,720 --> 00:43:43,240
♫ During the cold night, my yearning for you runs as a river ♫

492
00:43:43,240 --> 00:43:48,530
♫ And transforming into spring soil to nourish me ♫

493
00:43:48,530 --> 00:43:53,070
♫ The fleeting years fill up my lover’s sleeve ♫

494
00:43:53,070 --> 00:43:59,170
♫ Pieces of flowers and plants flow into the waters ♫

495
00:43:59,170 --> 00:44:04,610
♫ The cold will of heaven dresses in glittering colors of flowers ♫

496
00:44:04,610 --> 00:44:09,750
♫ And fall into the mortal realm to hurt my feelings ♫

497
00:44:09,750 --> 00:44:12,620
♫ Calamities are easy to overcome, but trials of love are difficult to overcome ♫

498
00:44:12,620 --> 00:44:21,920
♫ My depreciating heart still holds some hatred from my previous life ♫

499
00:44:28,560 --> 00:44:33,530
♫ The cold three lives and three worlds are as sudden
as a dream ♫

500
00:44:33,530 --> 00:44:39,030
♫ The wind dries my tears in those instantaneous years ♫

501
00:44:39,030 --> 00:44:43,480
♫ If we can no longer recognize our memories, ♫

502
00:44:43,480 --> 00:44:49,850
♫ Then allow our love to rest deep within the dust ♫

503
00:44:49,850 --> 00:44:55,170
♫ When will the cold ten miles of peach blossoms
bloom again? ♫

504
00:44:55,170 --> 00:45:00,510
♫ I see a gust of wind under the tree again ♫

505
00:45:00,510 --> 00:45:03,250
♫ Fallen blossoms are of love, flowing waters are of heartlessness ♫

506
00:45:03,250 --> 00:45:12,130
♫ Don’t allow our past grudges, love, and hate to chill the innocence of the flower ♫

507
00:45:13,870 --> 00:45:25,310
♫ My hope in this lifetime is to be with you ♫
